ENGLISH
1.cd /usr/bin
2.gedit (file_name) 
example : 
_________________________________________________________________________________________
gedit xampp
_________________________________________________________________________________________

3. Input ! 
_________________________________________________________________________________________
#! /bin/sh
gksu (path file.run adri app tersebut)
_________________________________________________________________________________________

Input Example :
_________________________________________________________________________________________
#! /bin/sh
gksu /opt/lampp/manager-linux-x64.run
_________________________________________________________________________________________
**note: You have to use gksu (afraid of error when use Python) if you want to get custom (if you don't have gksu just download)**

4. Finish





INDONESIA
1.cd /usr/bin
2.gedit (file_name) 
example : 
_________________________________________________________________________________________
gedit xampp
_________________________________________________________________________________________

3. Masukan 
_________________________________________________________________________________________
#! /bin/sh
gksu (path file.run adri app tersebut)
_________________________________________________________________________________________

Input Example :
_________________________________________________________________________________________
#! /bin/sh
gksu /opt/lampp/manager-linux-x64.run
_________________________________________________________________________________________
**note: Harus paka gksu (phyton takut error) kalau mau custom (kalo gk ada gksu download lah)**

4. Selesai
